These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, animation
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, train
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation |
| Transport     | train | quad-bike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, grapes
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey
1. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | lettuce      | grapes         |
| Sport   | basketball | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, juice
There 2 different types of food: onion, cranberry
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | juice | cola   |
| Food       | cranberry  | onion |

 #################################

 
